<title>USA: Loronix expects Q1 EPS loss.</title>
<headline>Loronix expects Q1 EPS loss.</headline>
<dateline>DURANGO, Colo. 1997-04-02</dateline>
<text>
<p>Loronix Information Systems Inc said Wednesday it expects to report a loss in the range of $0.09 to $0.11 per share for the first quarter, on reduced revenue.</p>
<p>The company said its first quarter results will be affected by a shortfall in imaging product sales and ramp-up costs incurred in establishing assembly operations for its CCTVware products and delays in shipping certain of these products.</p>
<p>For last year's first quarter, the company reported a profit of $0.04 per share.</p>
